					<span style="color:#8B9BB8;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:12px;">March 2026</span>
				</div>
				<h1 style="font-family:'Shippori Mincho','Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:clamp(26px,5vw,44px);font-weight:700;color:#F0EBE3;margin:0 0 20px 0;line-height:1.25;">4 Cruel Facts Japan Hides About the Battle of Okinawa</h1>
				<p style="color:#A8B8C8;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:16px;margin:0 0 16px 0;max-width:620px;line-height:1.8;">The history taught in Japanese classrooms is not the same history that Okinawans carry in their bones. Here are four facts that are systematically minimized — or erased entirely.</p>
				<p style="color:#8B9BB8;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin:0;">By <a href="/about/" style="color:#D4C9BC;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;">Shohei Toguchi</a></p>
			</div>
		</header>

		<!-- ARTICLE BODY -->
		<div style="padding:72px 32px 96px;background:#F0EBE3;">
			<div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;">

				<!-- Watch on YouTube CTA -->
				<div style="background:#1C2C4F;padding:20px 28px;margin-bottom:56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;border-left:4px solid #8B1D25;">
					<p style="color:#A8B8C8;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin:0;">Watch the short documentary on YouTube</p>
